{"tid":242440,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老母逼我講母親節快樂","createTime":"2017-05-14T02:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T02:25:59.000Z","uid":91936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffaa0999ddb4266af84730c6ceeaa9169f28fe5f","tid":242440,"uid":91936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"每逢母親節朝朝都懶係暗示咁<br />\n問我知唔知今日係咩日子<br />\n唔答佢又嬲9 講完母親節快樂又嬲9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱佢聽收音機講到啲母親節野<br />\n話無心情聽一野熄咗<br />\n過咗10秒又開返 較去第二個台<br />\n又係講母親節<br />\n又一野熄咗佢<br />\n即係點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次佢做呢啲咁明示嘅暗示我都即刻唔想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係唔想講呀<br />\n但係畀你聽到個無誠意嘅母親節快樂你會開心咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d34f307dfe59c8c7fca807e0e12d803669dcaf","tid":242440,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"求其啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ca28b11343a598990c704e0ce66eb27e4ff51d","tid":242440,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:25:59.000Z","msg":"講一句咁難咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}